data.description: WELCOME HOME!  This Semi Detached, One (1)  Family Frame "Treasure Island" Colonial Located In A Prime Bayside Neighborhood Is Situated On A Corner Plot With A Two (2) Car Detached Garage Is Waiting For Your Personal Touch! Create The Home You Always Wanted With The Convenience To Schools, Parks, Shopping, Restaurants, And The Best Part... It's In Close Proximity To All Means Of Transportation. The First Floor Offers A Spacious Living Room, Formal Dining Room, And Kitchen. The Second Floor Features Three (3) Bedrooms. There Is A Large Unfinished Basement With Storage, Laundry & Utilities. Hardwood Floors Throughout, With Plenty Of Natural Sunlight In All Rooms. Home Is Being Sold "As Is".  Don't Miss This Great Opportunity! Let's Make A Deal!
